column5: Killer spring as always, spent 90% of it chasing river giants, with the odd off day chasing trout, or panfish.                        Another nice day today, bring on the river smallies!
Those are some big cats. But were are the bbq and food pics?
You're lookin' svelte there Rich! Can't say the same for some of those hogs! No WGSF?? We have to start calling you the CatMaster. Thanks for sharing.
That is one very impressive cat!!! Would have been more impressive if you got it noodling.  Incredible report Rich!!!!
Some honkers there Rich  Are ya leavin those browns alone you used to catch so well?
Those cats are worthy of noodlin'.
Nice fat cats!!!! You are a shadow of your former self. Good for you. Keep up the reports.
Awesome report Rich You don't need to EAP those cats    They're HUGE
nice litter of kittens you got there a few nice carp too gratz!
Great seeing you around Rich! Nice fish!
God stuff Rich.  I haven't read one of your reports in a while.  This one was the cat's pajamas! (excuse the pun..)
Wow, those are some big ones, Rich- nice work!
Great stuff Rich.....still lookin' for a Kawartha report infested with greasy sammies and ice-cream though
awesome rich congrats on a great spring
Great stuff Rich. I've seen many of these on FB, but, they are definitely worth another look!!!  That one cat is amazing!!
